         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="30.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="1. There is a hero in the game which will continue to jump on it’s position and by pressing the “SPACE” key the hero will move forward." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="100.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="2. Everytime hero moves forward, he should land on an island." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="150.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="3. Hero can collide with orcs and he can kill the orcs by either making them fall into the abyss, by making them collide with a TNT or by killing them with some weapon." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
