               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="220.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="4. Hero will die if the hero fails to land on an island and falls into the abyss, if the hero comes under the orc, if the hero is in the range of TNT when the TNT bursts or if the hero is killed by Boss." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="300.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="5. If the hero dies in the game, you can use 100 coins to resurrect the hero in the game. But note that in a game, you can resurrect the hero only once." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="380.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="6. Hero must defeat the boss either by weapons or making the boss fall into the abyss to win the game." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
            <font>
               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="430.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="7. You can save a game, or load a previously saved game. " wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
