               <Font size="20.0" />
            </font>
         </Text>
         <Text layoutY="475.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="8. Hero can get weapons from the weapon chest. There are two kinds of weapons: Sword and TNT. There are also level upgradation of weapons which will make them even more powerful. Hero can use these to kill orcs." wrappingWidth="959.3768310546875">
